    "32 We could also show that some ZIFs exhibit very large negative thermal expansion (NTE), i.e., they contract upon heating.",
    "That phenomenon is counter-intuitive in dense materials, but actually quite common in framework materials such as some oxides, 33 zeolites, MOFs, etc.",
